Name:           python-azure-devops
Version:        6.0.0b4
Release:        0
Summary:        Python wrapper around the Azure DevOps 5x APIs
License:        MIT
Group:          Development/Languages/Python
URL:            https://github.com/Microsoft/vsts-python-api
